# Seanime requires no extra environment variables. 

# However, note that there will be 2 config.toml files. One here at ./config.toml, and another at ${DOCKER_DATA_DIR}/seanime/config.toml. T
# You should ignore the one in the data directory, only edit the one in the app directory. 

# In the config.toml, you can edit the password at [server].password
# View the full list of options at: https://seanime.app/docs/config
# Note: changes to the config.toml only require a restart i.e. docker compose restart seanime.